  <brief_title>Hospital Orientation Since SAMU Regulation Centre Call</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Association Between Clinical Criteria Collected at the SAMU Regulation Centre Call and the Hospital Orientation of Patients With Suspected Sepsis State</official_title>
